Mix whipped cream into filling ingredients.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Spread mixture over pie crust.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Refrigerate the pie for at least 4 hours or overnight. (If you\u2019re in a hurry, you could also freeze the pie for 1-2 hours.)\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Top with strawberries, cut, and serve.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"No-Bake Dulce De Leche Cheesecake Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chocolate cream cookie, butter, dulce de leche, cream cheese, vanilla extract, heavy cream, strawberry\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/74266f09d2a845f6a1d53559fd64027b/BFV10908_No-Bake_Dulce_De_Leche_Cheesecake_FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-09-27T20:13:30\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/8815/mp4_720x1280/1472568720\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"94\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"190\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/no-bake-chocolate-peanut-butter-cheesecake", "Title": "No-Bake Chocolate Peanut Butter Cheesecake", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"No-Bake Chocolate Peanut Butter Cheesecake Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/6d811916404d4be68a54f7e8359a4ed6/IMG_9609_2.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: graham cracker, butter, cream cheese, powdered sugar, vanilla extract, chocolate chips, peanut butter, confectioners sugar\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Desserts\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:47:28\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"8 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"10 graham crackers\"\n        \n          ,\"7 tablespoons melted butter\"\n        \n          ,\"24 ounces cream cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups powdered sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon vanilla extract\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups chocolate chips, melted\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups peanut butter, melted\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup confectioner\u2019s sugar\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place graham crackers into a plastic bag and crush them into fine crumbs with a rolling pin.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Pour the graham cracker crumbs into a bowl and combine with melted butter, mixing until the texture is like slightly wet sand.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Press the graham cracker crumbs in an even layer into the bottom of a 9-inch (23 cm) springform pan. Refrigerate.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large bowl, mix together softened cream cheese until smooth.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the powdered sugar and continue to mix until there are no lumps.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the vanilla and melted chocolate and mix until the color is even.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Pour the mixture over the graham cracker crust in the springform pan. Using a spatula or spoon, smooth the top. Refrigerate.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large bowl, mix together melted peanut butter and confectioner\u2019s sugar.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Pour mixture over cheesecake in springform pan. Use a knife or spatula to spread evenly and smooth the top.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Refrigerate for 2-4 hours.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"No-Bake Chocolate Peanut Butter Cheesecake Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: graham cracker, butter, cream cheese, powdered sugar, vanilla extract, chocolate chips, peanut butter, confectioners sugar\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/6d811916404d4be68a54f7e8359a4ed6/IMG_9609_2.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:47:28\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n    