y.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large skillet over medium heat, heat oil, then add cauliflower rice and let cook for 5 minutes., stirring occasionally.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add coconut milk, lime juice and lime zest, combine well and allow to cook until the liquid has evaporated.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Garnish with cilantro.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Coconut Lime Cauliflower Rice Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: cauliflower, coconut  oil, coconut milk, lime juice, lime, fresh cilantro\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/a021af60659e4ac590d5ef1641de63f6/BFV29238_VeggieRice4Ways_FB-Upload.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-09-28T16:33:10\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M56S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/54054/mp4_720x1280/1506622144\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"80\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"20\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/smoky-spiced-carrot-rice", "Title": "Smoky Spiced Carrot Rice", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Smoky Spiced Carrot Rice Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/a80abbfc02fb42cb9f5349438e94ace0/BFV29238_VeggieRice4Ways_FB-Upload.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: carrot, cooking oil, white onion, salt, pepper, garlic powder, smoked paprika, fresh parsley\",\n     \"keywords\": \"Veggie Rice, Vegetable Rice, Cauliflower Rice, Broccoli Rice, Carrot  Rice, Sweet Potato Rice, Sweet Potato Fried Rice, Fried Rice, Veggie \"rice\", vegetable \"rice\", riced veggies, riced vegetables, low carb, sides, rice, gluten-free, dairy-free, vegan, vegetarian, healthy, lighter, goodful, easy, fast\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-09-28T16:33:10\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"2 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 bunch carrots, peeled and sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon preferred cooking oil or water\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd white onion, diced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon garlic powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon smoked paprika\"\n        \n          ,\"Parsley, chopped, for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n   