{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/garlic-parmesan-broccoli-rice", "Title": "Garlic Parmesan Broccoli Rice", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Garlic Parmesan Broccoli Rice Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/62af8d0a0c924be1a5acb10f2b0e2597/BFV29238_VeggieRice4Ways_FB-Upload.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: broccoli, cooking oil, garlic, salt, pepper, grated parmesan cheese\",\n     \"keywords\": \"Veggie Rice, Vegetable Rice, Cauliflower Rice, Broccoli Rice, Carrot  Rice, Sweet Potato Rice, Sweet Potato Fried Rice, Fried Rice, Veggie \"rice\", vegetable \"rice\", riced veggies, riced vegetables, low carb, sides, rice, gluten-free, dairy-free, vegan, vegetarian, healthy, lighter, goodful, easy, fast\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-09-28T20:11:54\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"2 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 head broccoli, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon preferred cooking oil or water\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons grated Parmesan cheese, plus more for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a food processor, pulse the broccoli florets and stems until they reach your desired \u201crice\u201d consistency.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In pan over medium heat, add oil and garlic and cook for about 30 seconds.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add riced broccoli, salt, and pepper, and cook 5 minutes, or until tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add Parmesan and stir to combine.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve with a sprinkle of Parmesan.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Garlic Parmesan Broccoli Rice Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: broccoli, cooking oil, garlic, salt, pepper, grated parmesan cheese\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/62af8d0a0c924be1a5acb10f2b0e2597/BFV29238_VeggieRice4Ways_FB-Upload.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-09-28T20:11:54\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M56S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/54054/mp4_720x1280/1506622144\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"24\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/parchment-lemon-dill-salmon", "Title": "Parchment Lemon Dill Salmon", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Parchment Lemon Dill Salmon Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/6a81c7364ba5466e9df58488c513bf80/BFV10813_ParchmentBakedSalmon4Ways-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: asparagus, olive oil, salt, pepper, skinless salmon, white onion, lemon, fresh dill, parchment paper\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Seafood\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-10T23:42:21\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"1 serving\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"250 grams asparagus\"\n        \n          ,\"Olive oil to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt &amp; pepper to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"200 grams skinless salmon\"\n        \n          ,\"3 slices white onion\"\n        \n          ,\"2 slices lemon\"\n        \n          ,\"1 sprig fresh dill\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"Parchment paper or aluminum foil, 12\u00d718 inches (30x47cm)\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 350\u00b0F (180\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the parchment paper in half, then open up.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"On one half, lay down the asparagus. Drizzle on oil and sprinkle on salt &amp; pepper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Lay the salmon on the asparagus, and add more oil, salt, and pepper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place the onion, lemon, and dill on the salmon.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the parchment paper over the salmon, and cinch the paper together by folding it over itself along the edges.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 20 minutes or until internal temperature of salmon reaches 145\u02daF (63\u02daC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Parchment Lemon Dill Salmon Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: asparagus, olive oil, salt, pepper, skinless salmon, white onion, lemon, fresh dill, parchment paper\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/6a81c7364ba5466e9df58488c513bf80/BFV10813_ParchmentBakedSalmon4Ways-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-10T23:42:21\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/8250/mp4_720x1280/1472696613\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"96\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"41\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/parchment-garlic-butter-salmon", "Title": "Parchment Garlic Butter Salmon", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Parchment Garlic Butter Salmon Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/7d858a6019a440e0a6aad2c859098e51/BFV10813_ParchmentBakedSalmon4Ways-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: small white potato, butter, garlic, fresh parsley, salt, pepper, skinless salmon, parchment paper\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Seafood\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-10T23:42:22\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"1 serving\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 white potato, thinly sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons butter, melted\"\n        \n          ,\"1 clove garlic\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons fresh parsley, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt &amp; pepper to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"200 grams skinless salmon\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"Parchment paper or aluminum foil, 12\u00d718 inches (41x46cm)\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the oven to 350\u00b0F (180\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the parchment paper in half, then open up.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"On one half of the parchment, arrange the sliced potatoes. In a small bowl, combine the butter, garlic, and parsley. Drizzle half of the garlic butter mixture over the potatoes. Season with salt and pepper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Lay the salmon over the potatoes, and drizzle over the remaining garlic butter. Season with salt and pepper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the parchment paper over the salmon, and cinch the paper together by folding it over itself along the edges.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 30 minutes or until internal temperature of salmon reaches 145\u02daF (63\u02daC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Parchment Garlic Butter Salmon Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: small white potato, butter, garlic, fresh parsley, salt, pepper, skinless salmon, parchment paper\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/7d858a6019a440e0a6aad2c859098e51/BFV10813_ParchmentBakedSalmon4Ways-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-10T23:42:22\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/8250/mp4_720x1280/1472696613\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"99\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"183\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/sausage-spinach-tomato-rigatoni", "Title": "Sausage, Spinach, Tomato Rigatoni", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Sausage, Spinach, Tomato Rigatoni Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/d1d185b20fdd4e9181169d0115d348de/FinalFBforpkg.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, hot italian sausage, large yellow onion, garlic, salt, pepper, dried oregano, dried basil, dried parsley, tomato paste, diced tomato, grated parmesan cheese, spinach, rigatoni, ricotta cheese, fresh basil\",\n     \"keywords\": \"one-pot recipes, how to make, how to, recipe, pasta, italian sausage, spinach, tomato rigatoni, one pot pasta, creamy, chicken, wild, rice, wild rice, chicken thigh, chili, chipotle chili cornbread dumplings, yum, recipe, food, cook, how to, tasty, buzzfeed, best, easy, classic, yummy, best ever, perfect, ultimate, Easy recipes, how to cook, cooking, recipes, food, quick and easy, how to bake, baking,\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-05-01T23:04:16\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 tablespoon olive oil,\"\n        \n          ,\"5 hot Italian sausage links\"\n        \n          ,\"1 large yellow onion, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"5 garlic cloves, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon dried oregano\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon dried basil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon dried parsley\"\n        \n          ,\"12 ounces tomato paste\"\n        \n          ,\"15 ounces diced tomatoes\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups grated parmesan, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups spinach\"\n        \n          ,\"1 pound cooked rigatonis\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup ricotta cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"Basil to garnish.\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"To a large dutch oven on medium heat, add the olive oil and heat it until it shimmers.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the hot Italian sausage, cook until the the first side browns deeply, flip and cook on the other side until the sausage is fully cooked, 15 minutes. Remove the sausages from the pan and slice when they cool down.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"To the leftover pan drippings, add the chopped yellow onion, minced garlic, salt, pepper, dried basil, dried oregano, and dried parsley. Cook until the onions are caramelized and soft. About 10 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the tomato paste and cook until the tomato paste darkens slightly.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add in the diced tomatoes and the sausage slices into the pan, stir, and let the sauce come to a simmer.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add in half the grated parmesan, spinach, the cooked pasta, and stir to combine.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Spoon in fresh dollaps of the ricotta cheese, garnish with fresh basil, more grated parmesan, and serve!\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Sausage, Spinach, Tomato Rigatoni Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, hot italian sausage, large yellow onion, garlic, salt, pepper, dried oregano, dried basil, dried parsley, tomato paste, diced tomato, grated parmesan cheese, spinach, rigatoni, ricotta cheese, fresh basil\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/d1d185b20fdd4e9181169d0115d348de/FinalFBforpkg.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-05-01T23:04:16\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT04M20S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/92227/landscape_720/1525286591\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"68\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/one-pan-honey-lime-chicken", "Title": "One-Pan Honey Lime Chicken", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"One-Pan Honey Lime Chicken Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/11cace24d124495abd21e3b245a137bb/BFV18394_One-Pan_Chicken_Meal_Prep_4_Ways_-_FB_1080x1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: green bell pepper, red bell pepper, onion, olive oil, salt, pepper, chicken breast, parchment paper, honey, low sodium soy sauce, garlic, lime\",\n     \"keywords\": \"meal prep, goodful, chicken, asparagus, fajitas, bell peppers, onions, chicken and veggies, honey lime garlic, lemon pepper, caprese\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-11T23:05:09\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"\u00bd green bell pepper, sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd red bell pepper, sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc onion, sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"Olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 chicken breast\"\n        \n          ,\"Parchment paper\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoon honey\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon low-sodium soy sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"1 garlic clove, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 lime (half for the juice, half for slices)\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 450\u00b0F (230\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place bell peppers and onions into mixing bowl and thoroughly coat with olive oil, salt, and pepper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Tear off a sheet of parchment paper, large enough to fold into a packet.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Mix honey, garlic and soy sauce.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place bell peppers and chicken breast on top of parchment paper. Season with salt, and pepper, honey soy garlic sauce.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Squeeze lime juice on afterwards and garnish with lime slices.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the edges of the parchment paper widthwise 2-3 times then twist the ends until fully closed.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 20-25 minutes or until internal temperature reaches 165\u00b0F (74\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-Pan Honey Lime Chicken Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: green bell pepper, red bell pepper, onion, olive oil, salt, pepper, chicken breast, parchment paper, honey, low sodium soy sauce, garlic, lime\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/11cace24d124495abd21e3b245a137bb/BFV18394_One-Pan_Chicken_Meal_Prep_4_Ways_-_FB_1080x1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T23:05:09\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT02M25S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/28652/mp4_720x1280/1491583506\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"97\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"29\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/beef-broccoli-chow-mein", "Title": "Beef & Broccoli Chow Mein", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Beef &amp; Broccoli Chow Mein Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/1059154e5f5b43438edc6578cfdbd70a/BFV43733_ChowMein4Ways_FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: water, cornstarch, soy sauce, garlic, brown sugar, white pepper, flank steak, salt, cooking oil, chow mein noodle, onion, broccoli floret, sesame oil, scallions\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Chinese\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-06-01T23:54:31\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"\u00bd cup water\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon cornstarch\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup soy sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon minced garlic\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon brown sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon white pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"1 pound flank steak, thinly sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons cooking oil, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"1 6-ounce package Hong Kong-Style Pan-Fried (Chow Mein) Noodles, boiled according to package instructions\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup sliced onion\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup broccoli florets\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons sesame oil\"\n        \n          ,\"Sliced scallions, for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a 2-cup (480 ml) liquid measuring cup, combine the water, cornstarch, soy sauce, garlic, brown sugar, and white pepper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a medium bowl, season the steak strips with salt. Pour half of the sauce over the meat and set the rest aside for later. Mix the sauce with the steak, cover with plastic wrap, and marinate in the refrigerator for 30 minutes to 1 hour.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a wok or deep skillet over medium-high heat, heat 2 tablespoons of cooking oil, then add the par-cooked noodles. Cook for 1-2 minutes, allowing the noodles to crisp, then flip and cook for another 1-2 minutes. Transfer to a plate and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In the same wok, add 1 tablespoon of cooking oil and the marinated beef. Cook the beef for 3-4 minutes, then flip and cook for another 2 minutes, or until slightly crispy. Remove from the wok and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In the same wok, heat the remaining tablespoon of oil and add onion and broccoli. Season with salt, then stir and cook for 3-4 minutes, or until the onions are translucent.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Return the steak to the wok, followed by the crispy noodles and sesame oil. Mix well and pour in the reserved sauce. Toss gently and cook for another 2-3 minutes, or until everything is well-combined. Garnish with sliced scallions.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Beef &amp; Broccoli Chow Mein Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: water, cornstarch, soy sauce, garlic, brown sugar, white pepper, flank steak, salt, cooking oil, chow mein noodle, onion, broccoli floret, sesame oil, scallions\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/1059154e5f5b43438edc6578cfdbd70a/BFV43733_ChowMein4Ways_FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-06-01T23:54:31\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT04M55S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/97163/landscape_720/1528149276\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"97\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"113\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/slow-cooker-apple-spice-cobbler", "Title": "Slow-Cooker Apple Spice Cobbler", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Slow-Cooker Apple Spice Cobbler Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/62369.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: apple pie filling, spice cake mix, butter, vanilla ice cream\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Desserts\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-03-01T15:00:39\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"2  20z cans Apple Pie Filling\"\n        \n          ,\"1 Box Spice Cake Mix\"\n        \n          ,\"8oz Butter\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Combine the Apple Pie filling, cake mix, and butter in the slow cooker\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake on High for 2 to 2.5 hours\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Server a la mode with vanilla ice cream or your favorite whipped cream.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Slow-Cooker Apple Spice Cobbler Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: apple pie filling, spice cake mix, butter, vanilla ice cream\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/62369.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-03-01T15:00:39\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M24S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/35553/mp4_720x1280/1498683232\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"95\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"79\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/shredded-chicken-tacos", "Title": "Shredded Chicken Tacos", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Shredded Chicken Tacos Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/4e0273811ace44bdb6d93afdcd0c3cab/BFV36769_InstantPotDinners-FB1080x1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: boneless, skinless chicken breast, chili powder, ground cumin, pepper, garlic, salsa, tortilla, pico de gallo, guacamole, sour cream\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Mexican\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-02-16T17:17:53\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 boneless and skinless chicken breasts\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon chili powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon ground cumin\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups (or 1 16 ounce jar) salsa\"\n        \n          ,\"Tortillas, to serve\"\n        \n          ,\"Pico de gallo, to serve\"\n        \n          ,\"Guacamole, to serve\"\n        \n          ,\"Sour cream, to serve\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place chicken breasts inside the Instant Pot.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the chili powder, ground cumin, pepper, and garlic and toss until the chicken is coated on both sides. Add the salsa.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Seal the lid in place until you hear the beep. Tip: Closing the lid can be tricky. Have the pressure knob at 11 o\u2019clock and turn right.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Press \u201cPoultry\u201d and set time to 13 minutes. Set pressure knob to \u201cSealing\u201d.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Steam will release and the screen will say \u201cOn\u201d before it starts counting down.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Once the timer goes off, carefully turn the pressure knob to \u201cVenting\u201d. Let all of the stream release before opening the lid.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Shred the chicken with two forks.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve with tortillas, pico de gallo, guacamole, sour cream, or other desired toppings.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Shredded Chicken Tacos Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: boneless, skinless chicken breast, chili powder, ground cumin, pepper, garlic, salsa, tortilla, pico de gallo, guacamole, sour cream\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/4e0273811ace44bdb6d93afdcd0c3cab/BFV36769_InstantPotDinners-FB1080x1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-02-16T17:17:53\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT05M38S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/79548/landscape_720/1518807520\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"95\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"40\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/chicken-teriyaki-chow-mein", "Title": "Chicken Teriyaki Chow Mein", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Chicken Teriyaki Chow Mein Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/d7f0a66959f544f5b885f3bd993f072f/BFV43733_ChowMein4Ways_FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chicken breast, salt, pepper, teriyaki sauce, cooking oil, chow mein noodle, onion, carrot, broccoli floret, cabbage, sesame seeds\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Chinese\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-06-01T23:51:24\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 pound cubed chicken breast\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup teriyaki sauce, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"4 tablespoons cooking oil, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"1 6-ounce package Hong Kong-Style Pan-Fried (Chow Mein) Noodles, par cooked according to package instructions\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00be cup sliced onion\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup julienned carrots\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup broccoli florets\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup sliced green cabbage\"\n        \n          ,\"Sesame seeds, for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a medium bowl, season the cubed chicken with salt and pepper. Add \u00bc cup (of 60 ml) teriyaki sauce and mix until the chicken is well-coated. Cover with plastic wrap and marinate in the refrigerator for 30 minutes to 1 hour.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a wok or deep skillet over medium-high heat, heat 2 tablespoons of cooking oil, then add the par-cooked noodles. Cook for 1-2 minutes, allowing the noodles to crisp, then flip and cook for another 1-2 minutes. Transfer to a plate and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In the same wok, heat 1 tablespoon of cooking oil, then add the chicken. Cook for 3-4 minutes, until browned on one side, then stir and cook for another 3-4 minutes, until fully cooked through. Set the chicken aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In the same wok, add 1 tablespoon of oil, the onion, and carrot. Cook for 2-3 minutes, or until the onions are translucent. Add the broccoli and cabbage. Stir and cook for 1-2 minutes, then season with salt and pepper and cook for 3 minutes more, until the vegetables are soft.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the cooked chicken and crispy noodles back to the wok, along with the remaining \u00bc cup (60 ml) teriyaki sauce. Toss well and cook for 2-3 minutes, until everything is well-combined. Garnish with sesame seeds.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Chicken Teriyaki Chow Mein Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chicken breast, salt, pepper, teriyaki sauce, cooking oil, chow mein noodle, onion, carrot, broccoli floret, cabbage, sesame seeds\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/d7f0a66959f544f5b885f3bd993f072f/BFV43733_ChowMein4Ways_FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-