{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/healthy-slow-cooker-spinach-artichoke-dip", "Title": "Healthy Slow Cooker Spinach Artichoke Dip", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Healthy Slow Cooker Spinach Artichoke Dip Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/108216.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: reduced fat cream cheese, nonfat greek yogurt, canned artichoke heart, frozen spinach, low fat mozzarella cheese\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-10-19T16:16:37\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"10 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"8 ounces reduced fat cream cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup nonfat Greek yogurt\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups canned artichoke hearts, drained and chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups frozen spinach\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup low fat mozzarella cheese\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add all ingredients into a slow cooker and stir until combined\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cook on high for 4 hours, or until all cheese is melted\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Healthy Slow Cooker Spinach Artichoke Dip Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: reduced fat cream cheese, nonfat greek yogurt, canned artichoke heart, frozen spinach, low fat mozzarella cheese\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/108216.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-10-19T16:16:37\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M16S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/57253/mp4_720x1280/1508451314\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"93\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"38\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/rosemary-roasted-sweet-potatoes", "Title": "Rosemary Roasted Sweet Potatoes", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Rosemary Roasted Sweet Potatoes Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/87b2ebfa685841cca37454ea00111943/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: sweet potato, oil, dried rosemary, salt, pepper, fresh parsley\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 sweet potatoes\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon rosemary\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the oven to 400\u00b0F (200\u00baC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Slice the top and bottom off of the sweet potatoes, and slice potatoes in half crosswise. Rest each half on the broader end, then slice 3 times vertically and horizontally. Turn the potatoes on their side and make 4 or five more slices, to form cubes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer the sweet potatoes to a baking sheet, then add the oil, rosemary, salt, and pepper. Toss to coat evenly.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 35-40 minutes, until the sweet potatoes are tender and starting to brown around the edges.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Let cool for 5 minutes. Garnish with chopped parsley before serving.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Rosemary Roasted Sweet Potatoes Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: sweet potato, oil, dried rosemary, salt, pepper, fresh parsley\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/87b2ebfa685841cca37454ea00111943/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M48S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/31203/mp4_720x1280/1494349079\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"62\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/paprika-herb-roasted-carrots", "Title": "Paprika Herb Roasted Carrots", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Paprika Herb Roasted Carrots Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/40d6a3c9799f4ae68528d25591dab298/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: carrot, oil, Chopped fresh parsley, paprika, salt, pepper\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"4-5 carrots\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons oil\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup parsley\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons paprika\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the oven to 400\u00b0F (200\u00baC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Trim the carrots, then slice on the diagonal into \u00bd inch thick coins.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer the carrots to a baking sheet and add the oil, parsley, paprika, salt, and pepper. Toss to coat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 20-25 minutes, until the carrots are tender. Let cool for 5 minutes before serving.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Paprika Herb Roasted Carrots Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: carrot, oil, Chopped fresh parsley, paprika, salt, pepper\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/40d6a3c9799f4ae68528d25591dab298/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M48S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/31203/mp4_720x1280/1494349079\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"99\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"56\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/garlic-parmesan-roasted-broccoli", "Title": "Garlic Parmesan Roasted Broccoli", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Garlic Parmesan Roasted Broccoli Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/c903a3d7cb684325b525aa236e017022/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: broccoli, oil, lemon juice, vegetarian parmesan cheese, garlic powder, red pepper flakes, salt, pepper\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 heads broccoli\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon lemon juice\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup vegetarian parmesan\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons garlic powder\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon red pepper flakes\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 400\u00b0F (200\u00baC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Separate the crowns and snip off any leaves of the broccoli.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"On a prepared baking sheet, combine broccoli and remaining ingredients. Mix evenly.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 35-40 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Allow to cool for 5 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Garlic Parmesan Roasted Broccoli Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: broccoli, oil, lemon juice, vegetarian parmesan cheese, garlic powder, red pepper flakes, salt, pepper\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/c903a3d7cb684325b525aa236e017022/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M48S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/31203/mp4_720x1280/1494349079\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"99\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"90\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/one-pot-enchilada-rice", "Title": "One-pot Enchilada Rice", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"One-pot Enchilada Rice Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/0f555d126d9d45549414e1fbf6dbdc49/Thumb_B.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: oil, minced garlic, red onion, bell pepper, tomato, water, rice, black beans, fresh cilantro, tomato sauce, chili powder, cumin, salt, pepper, shredded cheese, avocado\",\n     \"keywords\": \"one,pot,rice,enchilada,four,ways,dinner,snack,lunch\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Fusion\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:47:38\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 tablespoon oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup red onion, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup bell pepper, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup tomatoes, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cups water\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups rice\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup black beans\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon cilantro, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup tomato sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon chili powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon cumin\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup shredded cheese (optional)\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd avocado, cubed (garnish)\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 400\u00baF (200\u00baC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Put oil in a cast-iron skillet over medium heat. Add garlic and onion to skillet and stir until garlic is slightly golden and onion has softened.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add pepper and saut\u00e9 2-3 minutes or until peppers have softened.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add tomatoes and saut\u00e9 1 minute.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove sauteed vegetables and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Pour water into the skillet and wait for it to come to a boil.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add rice and stir for 12-15 minutes until rice is fluffier but still slightly tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Make a circle in the center of the rice and add your saut\u00e9ed vegetables and black beans to the skillet and mix.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add cilantro, tomato sauce, chili powder, cumin, salt, and pepper, and stir.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add cheese on top (optional).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake in a preheated oven for 20-25 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Allow to cool for 5 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Garnish with cilantro and avocado (optional).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-pot Enchilada Rice Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: oil, minced garlic, red onion, bell pepper, tomato, water, rice, black beans, fresh cilantro, tomato sauce, chili powder, cumin, salt, pepper, shredded cheese, avocado\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/0f555d126d9d45549414e1fbf6dbdc49/Thumb_B.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:47:38\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M20S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/21638/mp4_720x1280/1485200330\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"97\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"288\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/one-pot-pasta-primavera", "Title": "One-pot Pasta Primavera", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"One-pot Pasta Primavera Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/0dc8acd33df34132a3412441d1726e52/BFV8813_OnePotPastaPrimavera-ThumbA.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: broth, linguine, broccoli floret, asparagus, small onion, garlic, red pepper flakes, salt, pepper, olive oil, mushroom, heavy whipping cream, grated parmesan cheese, fresh parsley\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Italian\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:46:34\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"4 cups broth of your choice\"\n        \n          ,\"10 oz uncooked linguine\"\n        \n          ,\"10 oz broccoli florets\"\n        \n          ,\"1 pound asparagus, chopped into 1-inch pieces\"\n        \n          ,\"1 small onion, diced\"\n        \n          ,\"4 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd tsp red pepper flakes\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt &amp; pepper to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tsp olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"4 oz mushrooms, sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup heavy whipping cream\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup grated parmesan\"\n        \n          ,\"3 Tbsp. fresh parsley, finely chopped\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a pot over high heat, combine broth, linguine, broccoli, asparagus, onion, garlic, red pepper flakes, salt, pepper, and olive oil. Stir.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the mushrooms and bring to a boil.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Once at a boil, reduce heat to medium and cook the pasta for 10 minutes, continuously tossing with tongs.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the heavy cream, parmesan, and parsley, and toss for an additional 3 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"If the liquid hasn\u2019t been completely absorbed, let the pasta sit off the heat for an additional few minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-pot Pasta Primavera Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: broth, linguine, broccoli floret, asparagus, small onion, garlic, red pepper flakes, salt, pepper, olive oil, mushroom, heavy whipping cream, grated parmesan cheese, fresh parsley\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/0dc8acd33df34132a3412441d1726e52/BFV8813_OnePotPastaPrimavera-ThumbA.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:46:34\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M48S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/31970/mp4_720x1280/1495124952\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"66\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/easy-peasy-potato-curry", "Title": "Easy-Peasy Potato Curry", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Easy-Peasy Potato Curry Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/154693.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: vegetable oil, medium yellow onion, garlic, curry powder, paprika, cayenne, cumin powder, allspice, fresh ginger, black pepper, potato, chickpeas, vegetable broth, lemon juice, diced tomato, coconut milk, rice, naan bread, fresh cilantro\",\n     \"keywords\": \"curry, potatoes, chickpeas, vegetarian\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Indian\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-05-07T15:17:46\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"2 tablespoons vegetable oil\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"4 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"4 teaspoons curry powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd teaspoon paprika\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon cayenne\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons cumin powder\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon allspice\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons minced fresh ginger\"\n        \n          ,\"1/2 teaspoon black pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"2 pounds potatoes, peeled and cubed\"\n        \n          ,\"1 15-ounce can chickpeas, drained\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup vegetable broth\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon lemon juice\"\n        \n          ,\"1 14-ounce can diced tomatoes\"\n        \n          ,\"1 14-ounce can coconut milk\"\n        \n          ,\"Cooked rice, for serving\"\n        \n          ,\"Naan, for serving\"\n        \n          ,\"Chopped fresh cilantro, for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat until shimmering. Add the onion and saute for about 3 minutes, until translucent.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the garlic and saute for about 2 minutes, until fragrant.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the curry powder, paprika, cayenne, cumin, allspice, ginger, salt, and pepper. Stir and cook for about 2 minutes until the spices are fragrant.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the potatoes and mix well until well-coated in spices.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the chickpeas and stir to incorporate.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the broth, lemon juice, and tomatoes and stir, then pour in the coconut milk and stir to combine.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Increase the heat to high and bring the mixture to a simmer. Once bubbling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 15-20 minutes, until the potatoes are tender and easily pierced with a fork.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve with cooked rice and naan and garnish with fresh cilantro.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Easy-Peasy Potato Curry Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: vegetable oil, medium yellow onion, garlic, curry powder, paprika, cayenne, cumin powder, allspice, fresh ginger, black pepper, potato, chickpeas, vegetable broth, lemon juice, diced tomato, coconut milk, rice, naan bread, fresh cilantro\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/154693.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-05-07T15:17:46\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M31S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/92916/landscape_720/1525716343\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"96\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"320\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/one-pot-mexican-quinoa", "Title": "One-Pot Mexican Quinoa", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"One-Pot Mexican Quinoa Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/368ad363ced740d297ed476bb54ee890/EasyToPackVeganLunchesFBFinal.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: quinoa, water, salsa, cumin, black beans, frozen corn, salt, olive oil, avocado, garlic, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, pepper, water, tortilla\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-02-03T00:15:47\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 cup quinoa, rinsed\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups water or vegetable broth\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bc cups salsa\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon cumin\"\n        \n          ,\"1 15-ounce can black beans, drained and rinsed\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup frozen corn, defrosted\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Olive oil, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 avocado, mashed\"\n        \n          ,\"1 clove garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons lemon juice\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoon olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"4-6 tablespoons water\"\n        \n          ,\"Tortillas, to serve (optional)\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a medium saucepan, combine quinoa and water, and bring to a boil over high heat. Reduce heat to low, cover with a lid, and simmer for 10 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add in salsa and cumin, and cover for 5 more minutes or until quinoa is fluffy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add in black beans, corn, salt, and olive oil, and stir until combined.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"For the avocado dressing, combine avocado, garlic, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and pepper in liquid measuring cup and whisk until smooth.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Whisk in water a little bit at a time until desired consistency is reached. 6. For extra smooth consistency, process all ingredients in blender or food processor.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Portion out into 4 containers and refrigerate for up to 5 days.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-Pot Mexican Quinoa Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: quinoa, water, salsa, cumin, black beans, frozen corn, salt, olive oil, avocado, garlic, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, pepper, water, tortilla\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/368ad363ced740d297ed476bb54ee890/EasyToPackVeganLunchesFBFinal.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-02-03T00:15:47\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT04M11S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/76566/landscape_720/1517619562\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"99\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"229\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/honey-balsamic-roasted-brussel-sprouts", "Title": "Honey Balsamic Roasted Brussels Sprouts", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Honey Balsamic Roasted Brussels Sprouts Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/067471ca930943519465e981015d8ae3/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: brussels sprouts, oil, balsamic vinegar, honey, salt, pepper\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1\u00bd pounds Brussels sprouts\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons oil\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons honey\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 425\u00b0F (220\u00baC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Slice the stem off of the Brussels sprouts and then halve them.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"On a prepared baking sheet, combine Brussels sprouts and remaining ingredients. Mix evenly.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 15-20 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Allow to cool for 5 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Honey Balsamic Roasted Brussels Sprouts Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: brussels sprouts, oil, balsamic vinegar, honey, salt, pepper\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/067471ca930943519465e981015d8ae3/Tasty_-_Facebook_-_1080x1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-12T04:28:26\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M48S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/31203/mp4_720x1280/1494349079\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"115\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/one-pot-creamy-chicken-marsala-pasta", "Title": "One-Pot Creamy Chicken Marsala Pasta", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"One-Pot Creamy Chicken Marsala Pasta Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/eff71ec36b99489fbde949ba4e30642a/BFV12215_One-PotCreamyChickenMarsalaPasta-ThumbTextless1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, boneless, skinless chicken breast, white mushroom, white onion, chicken stock, heavy cream, marsala wine, penne pasta, shredded parmesan cheese, salt, pepper, fresh parsley\",\n     \"keywords\": \"mushroom, chicken, pasta, one-pot, creamy, marsala\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Italian\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:46:54\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 tablespoons olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 \u00bd pounds boneless skinless chicken breast, cut in chunks\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups sliced white or button mushrooms\"\n        \n          ,\"1 white onion, sliced\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cups chicken stock\"\n        \n          ,\"1 \u00bd cups heavy cream\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup Marsala wine*\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cups uncooked penne pasta\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup shredded parmesan cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"Fresh parsley (optional garnish)\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat a large pot over medium-high heat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add 2 tablespoons of olive oil and chicken breast. Season with salt and pepper to taste.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cook until chicken is no longer pink. Remove and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the remaining tablespoon of oil, and the mushrooms and onion. Season with salt and pepper to taste. Cook until onions are browned, stirring occasionally.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Return the chicken to the pot. Add the stock, cream, wine, and pasta, bring up to a simmer, and cover.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"*Marsala wine can be purchased at most grocery stores near the dessert or sweet wines and gives the dish a distinct flavor. However, if you can\u2019t get your hands on Marsala, you can substitute 1 cup of white wine (240 ml) plus 1 \u00bd tablespoons of brandy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Simmer until pasta is tender, about 15-20 minutes, stirring occasionally.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"When pasta is tender, stir in parmesan cheese until smooth. Remove from heat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Garnish with fresh parsley.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-Pot Creamy Chicken Marsala Pasta Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, boneless, skinless chicken breast, white mushroom, white onion, chicken stock, heavy cream, marsala wine, penne pasta, shredded parmesan cheese, salt, pepper, fresh parsley\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/eff71ec36b99489fbde949ba4e30642a/BFV12215_One-PotCreamyChickenMarsalaPasta-ThumbTextless1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:46:54\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/9643/mp4_720x1280/1473178185\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"97\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"186\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/20-minute-one-pan-pizza", "Title": "20-Minute One-Pan Pizza", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"20-Minute One-Pan Pizza Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/180890.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: warm water, olive oil, all purpose flour, sugar, instant yeast, salt, marinara sauce, shredded mozzarella cheese, pepperoni slices, fresh basil\",\n     \"keywords\": \"Pizza, easy, from scratch, 20 minutes, quick dinner, easy dinner, pepperoni, mozzarella, marinara sauce, Tasty, basil, kid friendly, dinner for kids  \"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Fusion\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-09-27T18:21:44\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"2 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"\u00bd cup warm water\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"\u2154 cup all-purpose flour\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon instant yeast\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon salt\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup marinara sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups shredded mozzarella cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup pepperoni slices\"\n        \n          ,\"Chopped fresh basil, for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large nonstick pan, combine the warm water, olive oil, flour, sugar, yeast, and salt. Use a spatula to stir the ingredients, then smooth the dough to the edges of the pan.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Spread the marinara sauce over the dough, all the way to the edges. Sprinkle the mozzarella evenly over the sauce, then top with the pepperoni.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place over medium heat, cover, and cook for 10 minutes with the vent covered.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Uncover the vent and cook for 5 more minutes, until the edges are crispy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Slide the pizza out of the pan onto a cutting board and let cool for 5 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Sprinkle with basil, then slice and serve.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"20-Minute One-Pan Pizza Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: warm water, olive oil, all purpose flour, sugar, instant yeast, salt, marinara sauce, shredded mozzarella cheese, pepperoni slices, fresh basil\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/180890.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-09-27T18:21:44\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M17S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/110562/landscape_720/1538073269\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"98\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"242\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/pad-thai-carbonara", "Title": "Pad Thai Carbonara", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Pad Thai Carbonara Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/609eae942a304a0e9c2bf46fdc0c2631/BFV33355_HongThaimeeTastyStory-FB.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: wide rice noodle, palm sugar, fish sauce, tamarind paste, pork belly, oil, garlic, shallot, pickled turnip, egg, tofu, green onion, bean sprout, egg yolk, lime, peanuts, red thai chile\",\n     \"keywords\": \"pad thai, hong thaimee, thai food, thai cuisine, fish sauce, tamarind paste, chicken, palm sugar, chiles, spices, tofu, rice noodles, lime, peanuts, pork belly, egg yolk, asian, asian cuisine, southeast asia, carbonara\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Fusion\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-01-08T18:48:51\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"\u00bd pound wide rice noodles\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup palm sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup fish sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup tamarind paste\"\n        \n          ,\"6 ounces pork belly, cubed\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon oil\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 shallots, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pickled turnip, optional\"\n        \n          ,\"1 egg\"\n        \n          ,\"4 ounces tofu, cubed, optional\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd bunch Chinese chives or green onions, sliced, plus more for serving\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup bean sprouts, plus more for serving\"\n        \n          ,\"1 egg yolk\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Soak rice noodles in room temperature water 30 minutes prior to cooking.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a small saucepan over medium-high heat, whisk together palm sugar, tamarind paste, and fish sauce. Bring to a boil, reduce heat, and reduce for 5 minutes until the sauce thickens and coats the back of a wooden spoon. Remove sauce from heat and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat a cast-iron pan or wok over high heat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add pork belly and sear for about 3 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add oil, minced garlic, shallots, and turnips, and stir to incorporate.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Move the pork belly to the side of the pan and add the egg. Break the egg up with a spatula or wooden spoon and stir to scramble.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add soaked rice noodles and stir to evenly incorporate all ingredients, stirring for 1 to 2 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add 2 or 3 tablespoons of the reduced sauce and stir.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add tofu, Chinese chives or green onions, and bean sprouts. Stir to incorporate and remove from heat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"When plating, make a divot in the center of the noodles and add the egg yolk.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve immediately with lime, peanuts, more sprouts and chives, and red chiles, if desired.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Pad Thai Carbonara Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: wide rice noodle, palm sugar, fish sauce, tamarind paste, pork belly, oil, garlic, shallot, pickled turnip, egg, tofu, green onion, bean sprout, egg yolk, lime, peanuts, red thai chile\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/609eae942a304a0e9c2bf46fdc0c2631/BFV33355_HongThaimeeTastyStory-FB.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-01-08T18:48:51\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT02M23S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/71654/landscape_720/1515438443\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"3\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/lasagna-soup", "Title": "Lasagna Soup", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Lasagna Soup Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/7041188b99254834baa326731d068eb0/One-PotVeganDinnersFBFinal.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, onion, garlic, tomato paste, dried basil, dried oregano, crushed tomato, vegetable broth, green lentil, lasagna noodle, spinach, fresh basil\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-03-02T22:13:31\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 tablespoon olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 onion, diced\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons tomato paste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon dried basil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon dried oregano\"\n        \n          ,\"28 ounces crushed tomatoes\"\n        \n          ,\"6 cups vegetable broth\"\n        \n          ,\"\u2153 cup green lentils, rinsed\"\n        \n          ,\"8 ounces lasagna noodles, uncooked\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cups spinach\"\n        \n          ,\"Chiffonade basil, for serving\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large pot, heat the olive oil over medium heat. Once the oil begins to shimmer, add the onion and cook for 3-4 minutes, until semi-translucent.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the garlic, tomato paste, basil, and oregano, and cook for 2-3 more minutes, or until the onions are translucent and herbs are fragrant.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the crushed tomatoes, vegetable broth, and lentils, and bring to a boil. Increase heat to medium-high and cook for 10 minutes or until lentils are halfway tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Break apart the lasagna noodles into about 2-inch-long (5-cm) pieces and add to the pot. Let the soup cook for another 10-15 minutes, or until the pasta is al dente and the lentils are tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Stir in the spinach and let wilt, then serve immediately.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Lasagna Soup Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, onion, garlic, tomato paste, dried basil, dried oregano, crushed tomato, vegetable broth, green lentil, lasagna noodle, spinach, fresh basil\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/7041188b99254834baa326731d068eb0/One-PotVeganDinnersFBFinal.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-03-02T22:13:31\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT04M17S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/82307/landscape_720/1520041477\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"98\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"354\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/southwestern-style-quinoa-salad", "Title": "Southwestern-style Quinoa Salad", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Southwestern-style Quinoa Salad Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/8c49611d7f6740d3bdf7195f79460fdd/Facebook.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: vegetable oil, garlic, jalape\u00f1o, black beans, corn, roma tomato, quinoa, vegetable stock, chili powder, cumin, salt, pepper, avocado, lime, fresh cilantro\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Mexican\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-09-01T17:09:30\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"2 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"2 tablespoons oil\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 jalepe\u00f1o, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"15 ounces black beans\"\n        \n          ,\"15 ounces corn\"\n        \n          ,\"3 roma tomatoes, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup quinoa\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups vegetable stock\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon chili powder\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons cumin\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"1 avocado, cubed\"\n        \n          ,\"1 lime, juiced\"\n        \n          ,\"Cilantro, to garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat the oil in a large pan over medium heat. Add the garlic and jalape\u00f1o and cook for about 2 minutes, until softened.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the black beans, corn, tomatoes, quinoa, vegetable stock, chili powder, cumin, salt, and pepper. Stir, then cover and cook for 15-20 minutes, until the liquid is absorbed and the quinoa is tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer the salad to a serving bowl and top with the avocado, lime juice, and cilantro.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Southwestern-style Quinoa Salad Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: vegetable oil, garlic, jalape\u00f1o, black beans, corn, roma tomato, quinoa, vegetable stock, chili powder, cumin, salt, pepper, avocado, lime, fresh cilantro\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/8c49611d7f6740d3bdf7195f79460fdd/Facebook.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-09-01T17:09:30\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT02M19S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/50638/mp4_720x1280/1504219940\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"98\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"273\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/easy-one-pot-mac-n-cheese", "Title": "Easy One-pot Mac \u2018n\u2019 Cheese", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Easy One-pot Mac \u2018n\u2019 Cheese Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/3c0710e0531b41b7804acf4a52ee15be/FB_04forpkg.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: whole milk, elbow macaroni, butter, cheddar cheese, salt, pepper, fresh parsley\",\n     \"keywords\": \"mac and cheese, mac n cheese, macaroni, cheese, cheesy, elbow, cheddar, milk, noodles, pasta, butter, flour, parsley, salt, pepper, bacon, panko, bread crumbs, garlic, chives, colby jack, provolone, mozzarella, Gouda, Gruyere, yum, recipe, food, cook, how to, tasty, buzzfeed, best, easy, classic, yummy, best ever, perfect, ultimate\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Sides\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-11-21T19:31:22\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"5 cups whole milk\"\n        \n          ,\"1 box elbow macaroni\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup butter\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups cheddar cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Parsley, to serve\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large pot on medium-high heat, gently heat the milk to a simmer.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add in the elbow macaroni. Cook until the pasta is tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Once the noodles are cooked, turn off the heat. Add in the butter, cheddar, salt, and pepper. Fold these ingredients with the pasta until the cheese and butter melt into the milk to create a thick sauce.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Sprinkle with parsley and serve!\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Easy One-pot Mac \u2018n\u2019 Cheese Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: whole milk, elbow macaroni, butter, cheddar cheese, salt, pepper, fresh parsley\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/3c0710e0531b41b7804acf4a52ee15be/FB_04forpkg.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-11-21T19:31:22\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT02M43S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/64207/mp4_720x1280/1511818798\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"93\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"823\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/one-pot-butternut-squash-pilaf", "Title": "One-Pot Butternut Squash Pilaf", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"One-Pot Butternut Squash Pilaf Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/1ffeadeed97b450b9092f65c72da511f/OnePotButternutSquashPilafFBMOSTFINAL.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, small yellow onion, garlic, fresh thyme, arborio rice, salt, pepper, dry white wine, butternut squash, vegetable broth, fresh parsley\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-01-25T17:39:53\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"2 tablespoons olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 small yellow onion, diced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon thyme\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups arborio rice\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup dry white wine\"\n        \n          ,\"4 cups butternut squash, cubed\"\n        \n          ,\"4 cups vegetable broth\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"To prep cut off both ends of the butternut squash and poke 10-15 air vents with a fork. Microwave on high for 3-4 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Peel the skin off of the squash. The skin should peel right off! Once peeled, cut into 1x1-inch (2x2-cm) cubes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 375\u00b0F (190\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large dutch oven or oven-safe pot, saut\u00e9 onion in olive oil for 3-4 minutes or until semi-translucent. Add garlic and saut\u00e9 for 2 more minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the thyme and cook for 2 minutes, until fragrant.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add arborio rice and saut\u00e9 until lightly toasted, then stir in salt, pepper and white wine.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Stir in butternut squash and and vegetable broth and bring to a boil.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cover pot and transfer to oven. Bake for 15-20 minutes, until liquid is absorbed.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Garnish with parsley and serve immediately\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-Pot Butternut Squash Pilaf Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, small yellow onion, garlic, fresh thyme, arborio rice, salt, pepper, dry white wine, butternut squash, vegetable broth, fresh parsley\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/1ffeadeed97b450b9092f65c72da511f/OnePotButternutSquashPilafFBMOSTFINAL.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-01-25T17:39:53\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M36S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/74801/landscape_720/1516902374\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"99\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"56\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/creamy-dairy-free-one-pot-pasta", "Title": "Creamy Dairy-free One Pot Pasta", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Creamy Dairy-free One Pot Pasta Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/96a1946030be40fa80ea4d0ebdc8bc20/EasyVeganWeeknightDinnersFBFinalNEW.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, onion, garlic, tomato paste, grape tomato, salt, pepper, vegetable broth, non-dairy milk, dried pasta, fresh spinach, nutritional yeast\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Dinner\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-12-14T15:14:49\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"Olive oil, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 onion, diced\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons tomato paste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 pint cherry tomatoes, halved\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"2\u00bd cups vegetable broth\"\n        \n          ,\"2\u00bd cups non-dairy milk\"\n        \n          ,\"16 ounces dried pasta\"\n        \n          ,\"5 ounces spinach\"\n        \n          ,\"\u2153 cup nutritional yeast\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large pot over medium heat, add the olive oil and onion and cook for 3-5 minutes until semi-translucent.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the garlic and tomato paste and cook for 3 more minutes, stirring occasionally.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the tomatoes and cook for 3-5 more minutes, until the skins begin to wrinkle and tomatoes begin to release liquid.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Season with salt and pepper, than add the vegetable broth, non-dairy milk, and pasta and stir until combined.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bring to a boil, then cover, reduce heat, and let simmer for 10 minutes or until most liquid is absorbed.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the spinach and stir until wilted.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the nutritional yeast and stir until combined.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove from heat and serve immediately.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Creamy Dairy-free One Pot Pasta Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: olive oil, onion, garlic, tomato paste, grape tomato, salt, pepper, vegetable broth, non-dairy milk, dried pasta, fresh spinach, nutritional yeast\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/96a1946030be40fa80ea4d0ebdc8bc20/EasyVeganWeeknightDinnersFBFinalNEW.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-12-14T15:14:49\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT04M52S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/71147/landscape_720/1515090534\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"96\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"274\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/veggie-packed-one-pot-split-pea-soup", "Title": "Veggie-Packed One-Pot Split Pea Soup", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Veggie-Packed One-Pot Split Pea Soup Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/128106.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: sourdough loaf, olive oil, onion, carrot, celery, garlic, split peas, dried thyme, salt, pepper, turmeric, red pepper flakes, potato, vegetable stock, bay leaf\",\n   \n     \"cookTime\": \"PT70M\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-01-03T21:36:07\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"12 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 sourdough loaf\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"2 onions, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"2 carrots, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"3 celery stalks, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2\u00bd cups split peas\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon thyme\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon turmeric\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon red pepper flakes\"\n        \n          ,\"3 potatoes, peeled, cubed\"\n        \n          ,\"8 cups vegetable stock\"\n        \n          ,\"2 bay leaves\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"On a cutting board, place the loaf of bread on its side and slice off the top portion. Using a small knife, cut around the inside of the bread, being careful not to cut through the sides, and scoop out the center of the roll. Save this for dipping later on or use for bread crumbs.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large soup pot, combine the olive oil, onions, carrots, and celery, and cook 5 minutes over medium heat until onions are translucent.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the garlic and cook 2 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the split peas, thyme, salt, pepper, tumeric, and red pepper flakes, and stir until well combined.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the vegetable stock and bay leaves, cover with a lid and cook for 40 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add potatoes, then cover and cook 20 more minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove bay leaves and serve soup in your bread bowl.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Veggie-Packed One-Pot Split Pea Soup Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: sourdough loaf, olive oil, onion, carrot, celery, garlic, split peas, dried thyme, salt, pepper, turmeric, red pepper flakes, potato, vegetable stock, bay leaf\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/128106.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-01-03T21:36:07\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M35S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n    