l sauce ingredients in a small bowl.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat oil over a nonstick pan and add shrimp stirring until cooked.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Pour sauce in pan and stir to coat meat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Once the sauce is bubbling, add the veggies to the pan and stir again to coat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cook until meat is cooked through and veggies are soft.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve over rice or alone.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"One-Pan Shrimp And Green Bean Stir-fry Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: shrimp, salt, pepper, broccoli, green beans, carrot, soy sauce, honey, garlic, ginger, sesame seed\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/dd17edff5396456a8ed438c170487744/BFV16130_Stir-Fry_4_Ways_FB.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T20:52:21\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/20739/mp4_720x1280/1484338324\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"92\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"45\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/sweet-potato-pizza-bites", "Title": "Sweet Potato Pizza Bites", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Sweet Potato Pizza Bites Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/32778292ca2b4b7c892151d379299747/BFV39745_Low-StressDinners_FB.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: sweet potato, olive oil, salt, pepper, marinara sauce, pesto, shredded mozzarella cheese, fresh basil\",\n     \"keywords\": \"Low-Stress, Low-Stress Dinners, one pan, one pan dinners, steak fajitas, jambalaya, tuscan white beans, sweet potato pizza bites, family dinner, easy dinner, quick dinner, fast easy dinner, easy healthy dinner, healthy family dinner, healthy family recipe\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-03-17T00:02:56\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"4 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 medium sweet potatoes\"\n        \n          ,\"Olive oil, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup marinara sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup pesto\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup shredded mozzarella\"\n        \n          ,\"Fresh basil, for garnish\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the oven to 375\u00b0F (190\u00b0C). Line two baking sheets with parchment paper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Carefully slice the sweet potatoes into \u00bd-inch (1 cm) rounds.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer the sweet potato rounds to a large bowl. Drizzle with olive oil and season with salt and pepper. Stir to coat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer the rounds to the baking sheets, spacing evenly.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 30 minutes, flipping halfway, until golden brown.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Top the sweet potato rounds with marinara sauce and mozzarella, or pesto and mozzarella.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for another 5 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and the sauce is warmed through.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Garnish with fresh basil and serve.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Sweet Potato Pizza Bites Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: sweet potato, olive oil, salt, pepper, marinara sauce, pesto, shredded mozzarella cheese, fresh basil\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/32778292ca2b4b7c892151d379299747/BFV39745_Low-StressDinners_FB.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-03-17T00:02:56\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT04M01S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/85393/landscape_720/1521485033\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingV