: \"Bake for 15 minutes, until golden brown and flaky.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Pigs In A Blanket Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: puff pastry, hot dog, cheddar cheese\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/eb3907e9c5024f9da7b422958bd751f1/BFV11486_3IngredientAppetizers-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T13:28:50\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/7967/mp4_720x1280/1472163621\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"96\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"106\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
