{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/egg-roll-mozzarella-sticks", "Title": "Egg Roll Mozzarella Sticks", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Egg Roll Mozzarella Sticks Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/45989167495e491e8032cf38cf51b0c9/BFV11486_3IngredientAppetizers-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: egg roll wrapper, string cheese, water, oil, marinara sauce\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Deep-Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-11T13:28:49\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"10 sticks\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"5 egg roll wrappers\"\n        \n          ,\"10 sticks string cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"Water\"\n        \n          ,\"Oil, for frying\"\n        \n          ,\"Marinara sauce\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Slice the egg roll wrappers in half.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place a stick of string cheese on the edge of the egg roll wrapper, then fold the sides of the wrapper over the ends of the cheese.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Wet the other edge of the wrapper with water, then roll it up tightly, pressing the edge to make sure it\u2019s sealed.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Repeat with the remaining wrappers and cheese.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat oil in a pot.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fry the sticks until golden brown, then drain on a paper towel.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve with marinara.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Egg Roll Mozzarella Sticks Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: egg roll wrapper, string cheese, water, oil, marinara sauce\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/45989167495e491e8032cf38cf51b0c9/BFV11486_3IngredientAppetizers-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T13:28:49\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/7967/mp4_720x1280/1472163621\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"93\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"38\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/jalapeno-poppers", "Title": "Jalape\u00f1o Poppers", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Jalape\u00f1o Poppers Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/f5ca94bf8118491dbdbc1c2977ce75cc/BFV11486_3IngredientAppetizers-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: jalape\u00f1o, bacon, cream cheese\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-11T13:28:50\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"8 poppers\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"4 jalape\u00f1os\"\n        \n          ,\"8 slices bacon\"\n        \n          ,\"8 ounces cream cheese, softened\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 400\u00b0F (200\u02daC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Slice the jalape\u00f1os in half, then remove the seeds by scraping out the insides.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Spread the cream cheese evenly among the jalape\u00f1o shells.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Wrap each jalape\u00f1o in bacon.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place the bacon-wrapped jalape\u00f1os on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper. Bake for 20 minutes, until bacon is browned and peppers are tender.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Jalape\u00f1o Poppers Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: jalape\u00f1o, bacon, cream cheese\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/f5ca94bf8118491dbdbc1c2977ce75cc/BFV11486_3IngredientAppetizers-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T13:28:50\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/7967/mp4_720x1280/1472163621\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"99\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"172\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/homemade-soft-pretzels", "Title": "Homemade Soft Pretzels", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Homemade Soft Pretzels Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/7fb7505220bc43be812c2c22f744625b/pretzel-thumb2.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: water, salt, sugar, active dry yeast, flour, oil, baking soda, egg, coarse salt\",\n     \"keywords\": \"pretzel, homemade, snack\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-08-03T00:24:46\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"8 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1\u00bd cups warm water\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"1 packet dry active yeast\"\n        \n          ,\"4\u00bd cups flour\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons oil, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"\u2154 cup baking soda\"\n        \n          ,\"2 eggs, beaten\"\n        \n          ,\"Coarse salt\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a bowl, mix water, salt, and sugar until combined. Add yeast, and let rest 5 minutes until yeast starts to foam.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add flour and 2 tablespoons of oil, and mix thoroughly until a dough forms.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove the dough and use the remaining oil to cover the bowl.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cover bowl with plastic wrap, and leave in a warm place for 1 hour.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 450\u00b0F (230\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cut dough into 8 pieces and roll them out into thin ropes, twisting the two ends to form a pretzel shape.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add baking soda to a large pot of water, and bring to a rolling boil. Boil each pretzel for 30 seconds per side.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer pretzels to a baking sheet, brush with egg wash, and sprinkle with salt. Bake for 10-15 minutes, until golden brown.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Homemade Soft Pretzels Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: water, salt, sugar, active dry yeast, flour, oil, baking soda, egg, coarse salt\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/7fb7505220bc43be812c2c22f744625b/pretzel-thumb2.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-08-03T00:24:46\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M38S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/46102/mp4_720x1280/1501776624\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"94\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"325\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/cheese-stuffed-garlic-parmesan-pretzels", "Title": "Cheese-stuffed Garlic Parmesan Pretzels", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Cheese-stuffed Garlic Parmesan Pretzels Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/d642d37450d747f69992fa0c2652d3e1/BFV15825_Cheese-StuffedGarlicParmesanPretzels_ThumbA.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: pizza dough, shredded mozzarella cheese, butter, garlic, fresh parsley, shredded parmesan cheese\",\n     \"keywords\": \"cheese, pretzel, garlic parmesan, garlic, parmesan, stuffed, buzzfeed, tasty, delicious, buzzfeed tasty, game day, reicpe, mozzarella\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:47:30\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"8 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 13.8-ounce can pizza dough\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cups mozzarella, shredded\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons butter, melted\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons fresh parsley, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup parmesan, shredded\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 400\u02daF (200\u02daC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Stretch pizza dough out into a rectangle.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cut into 8 equal-sized strips.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Stretch strips lengthwise, and widthwise.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place mozzarella down the middle of each strip.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold and pinch the dough around the cheese along the entire strip, ensuring to close off the ends.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Form a pretzel shape by taking the ends of the strip, making a \u201cU\u201d shape, twisting the ends around each other twice and connecting the ends to the bottom of the \u201cU\u201d shape.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer to a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Mix melted butter, garlic, and parsley and pour onto pretzels.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Sprinkle parmesan evenly on top of the pretzels.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 20 minutes or until golden brown.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Cheese-stuffed Garlic Parmesan Pretzels Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: pizza dough, shredded mozzarella cheese, butter, garlic, fresh parsley, shredded parmesan cheese\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/d642d37450d747f69992fa0c2652d3e1/BFV15825_Cheese-StuffedGarlicParmesanPretzels_ThumbA.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:47:30\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/19597/mp4_720x1280/1483032312\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"96\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"45\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/cheese-stuffed-pizza-pretzels", "Title": "Cheese-stuffed Pizza Pretzels", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Cheese-stuffed Pizza Pretzels Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/2ed51e00ab60424fa5b1ec85b40a9e6f/BFV5628_CheeseStuffedPizzaPretzels-Thumb1080SQ.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: store-bought pizza dough, shredded mozzarella cheese, presliced pepperoni, marinara sauce, nonstick vegetable oil cooking spray\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Fusion\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:46:18\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"3 pretzels\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 (13.8-ounce) tube store-bought pizza dough\"\n        \n          ,\"4 cups shredded mozzarella (from two 8-ounce bags)\"\n        \n          ,\"15 presliced pepperoni\"\n        \n          ,\"Store-bought marinara or pizza sauce for dipping\"\n        \n          ,\"nonstick vegetable oil spray\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 425\u00b0F (220\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Unroll the dough, it should form 15x9-inch (38x22 cm) rectangle, then cut the rectangle horizontally into three equal strips. (These will be your three pretzels.)\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Carefully stretch each of the strips by width and length \u2014 stretch each to about 3 inch (7 \u00bd cm) width and about 34 inch (86 cm) length.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Sprinkle 1 cup (100g) of cheese down the center of each dough strip. Reserve the last 1 cup (100g) of cheese for later.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the dough over the cheese, pressing to seal and rolling slightly to create 3 dough logs filled with cheese.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Cover a baking sheet with foil and spray with vegetable oil.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"To form the pretzels, take one dough log, move it to the foil covered baking sheet, then form a circle with the ends of the log at the top of the circle. Twist the log ends around each other once and bring them down to meet the bottom of the circle. Repeat with the other two dough logs.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Wrap pepperonis on the pretzels \u2014 5-ish per pretzel \u2014 then sprinkle the remaining cup of cheese among the three pretzels.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake 14-18 minutes until deep golden brown.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve immediately with pizza sauce for dipping.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Cheese-stuffed Pizza Pretzels Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: store-bought pizza dough, shredded mozzarella cheese, presliced pepperoni, marinara sauce, nonstick vegetable oil cooking spray\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/2ed51e00ab60424fa5b1ec85b40a9e6f/BFV5628_CheeseStuffedPizzaPretzels-Thumb1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:46:18\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M43S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/32065/mp4_720x1280/1495125053\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"93\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"83\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/chicken-salad-sliders", "Title": "Chicken Salad Sliders", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Chicken Salad Sliders Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/55b1a5c4d7ec4cc582da6be55c2701db/BFV31032Siders2Ways_FBfinal.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chicken, paprika, cayenne pepper, onion powder, garlic powder, pepper, salt, celery, fresh chives, fresh dill, lemon juice, mayonnaise, sour cream, dijon mustard, slider bun, bacon, lettuce\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Lunch\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-10-17T18:02:11\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"12 sliders\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 cups cooked chicken, shredded\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon paprika\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup cayenne pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon onion powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon garlic powder\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup celery, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup chives, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons dill, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons lemon juice\"\n        \n          ,\"\u2153 cup mayonnaise\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup sour cream\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons Dijon mustard\"\n        \n          ,\"12 slider buns\"\n        \n          ,\"1 pound bacon, cooked, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"Lettuce, chopped\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a bowl, mix together chicken, paprika, cayenne pepper, onion powder, garlic powder, pepper, salt, celery, chives, dill, lemon juice, mayonnaise, sour cream, and Dijon mustard.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place chicken salad mixture on a slider bun. Top with bacon and lettuce. Place top bun.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Chicken Salad Sliders Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chicken, paprika, cayenne pepper, onion powder, garlic powder, pepper, salt, celery, fresh chives, fresh dill, lemon juice, mayonnaise, sour cream, dijon mustard, slider bun, bacon, lettuce\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/55b1a5c4d7ec4cc582da6be55c2701db/BFV31032Siders2Ways_FBfinal.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-10-17T18:02:11\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M22S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/56760/mp4_720x1280/1508287730\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"82\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"11\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/bbq-pulled-chicken-sliders", "Title": "BBQ Pulled Chicken Sliders", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"BBQ Pulled Chicken Sliders Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/107761.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: slider bun, olive oil, BBQ sauce, lemon juice, onion powder, garlic powder, paprika, cayenne, pepper, salt, chicken, red cabbage, shredded carrot, green onion, jalape\u00f1o, paprika, pepper, garlic powder, salt, lemon juice, apple cider vinegar, olive oil, honey\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"BBQ\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-10-17T23:45:57\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"12 sliders\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"n/a\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups BBQ sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons lemon juice\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon onion powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon garlic powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon paprika\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc teaspoon cayenne\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cups cooked chicken, shredded\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"2 cups red cabbage, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd cups carrots, shredded\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup green onions, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons jalape\u00f1os chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon paprika\"\n        \n          ,\"Pepper to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon garlic powder\"\n        \n          ,\"Salt, to taste\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup lemon juice\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons apple cider vinegar\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup olive oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon honey\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Mix together cabbage, carrots, green onions, jalape\u00f1os, paprika, pepper, garlic powder, salt, lemon juice, apple cider vinegar, olive oil, and honey. Chill until ready to use.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat a skillet over medium heat. Add olive oil, BBQ sauce, lemon juice, onion powder, garlic powder, paprika, cayenne, pepper, and salt. Stir until sauce begins to bubble and thicken.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Mix in chicken and stir until fully incorporated.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place BBQ chicken on top of bottom slider bun. Top with slaw. Place top bun. Serve immediately.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"BBQ Pulled Chicken Sliders Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: slider bun, olive oil, BBQ sauce, lemon juice, onion powder, garlic powder, paprika, cayenne, pepper, salt, chicken, red cabbage, shredded carrot, green onion, jalape\u00f1o, paprika, pepper, garlic powder, salt, lemon juice, apple cider vinegar, olive oil, honey\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/107761.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-10-17T23:45:57\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M22S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/56760/mp4_720x1280/1508287730\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"100\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"18\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/bacon-chicken-wrapped-mozzarella-sticks", "Title": "Bacon Chicken Wrapped Mozzarella Sticks", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Bacon Chicken Wrapped Mozzarella Sticks Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/144821.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: ketchup, tomato sauce, apple cider vinegar, mustard, light brown sugar, granulated sugar, boneless, skinless chicken tender, mozzarella cheese, bacon, fresh parsley\",\n     \"keywords\": \"hot make bacon chicken wrapped mozzarella sticks, bacon mozzarella sticks, bacon wrapped chicken, bacon, chicken, string cheese, mozzarella sticks, BBQ sauce, tasty\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-03-19T20:03:48\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"8 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"2 cups ketchup\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup tomato sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup apple cider vinegar\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon mustard\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup light brown sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup granulated sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"8 boneless, skinless chicken tenders\"\n        \n          ,\"8 mozzarella cheese sticks\"\n        \n          ,\"8 slices of bacon\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon chopped parsley, for serving\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Make the marinade: In a medium dish or bowl, combine the ketchup, tomato sauce, apple cider vinegar, mustard, light brown sugar, and granulated sugar. Set aside \u00bd cup (130 g) of the mixture for the glaze and another \u00bd cup (130 g) for the dip.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Butterfly the chicken tenders. Place a large sheet of plastic wrap over them and gently use a meat mallet or rolling pin to flatten the chicken to about \u215b-inch (3 mm) thickness.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove the plastic wrap and place the chicken tenders in a the remaining marinade. Cover and refrigerate for one hour.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the oven to 400\u00b0F (200\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove chicken from the refrigerator. Wrap a chicken tender around a mozzarella cheese stick. Take a strip of bacon and spiral it around the tender. Repeat with remaining chicken tenders.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place the chicken tenders on a baking sheet. Bake for 20 minutes or until slightly crispy. Flip tenders halfway through.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove the tenders from the oven and generously brush with reserved glazed. Bake for another 10 minutes or until completely crisp.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove from the oven, top with chopped parsley, and serve with reserved dip\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Bacon Chicken Wrapped Mozzarella Sticks Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: ketchup, tomato sauce, apple cider vinegar, mustard, light brown sugar, granulated sugar, boneless, skinless chicken tender, mozzarella cheese, bacon, fresh parsley\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/144821.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-03-19T20:03:48\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M34S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/85449/landscape_720/1521492599\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"86\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"34\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/bbq-bacon-ice-tray-meatballs", "Title": "BBQ Bacon Ice Tray Meatballs", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"BBQ Bacon Ice Tray Meatballs Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/135759.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: ground beef, yellow onion, fresh parsley, bread crumbs, egg, garlic, dried oregano, dried basil, salt, pepper, bacon, BBQ sauce\",\n     \"keywords\": \"buzzfeed, tasty, BBQ, bacon, beef, meatball, ice tray, party, \"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-02-08T00:34:00\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"24 balls\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 pound ground beef\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd yellow onion, diced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup parsley, chopped\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup bread crumbs\"\n        \n          ,\"1 egg\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon dried oregano\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon dried basil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon salt\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd teaspoon pepper\"\n        \n          ,\"18 slices bacon\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup barbecue sauce\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a medium-sized bowl, mix the ground beef, onion, parsley, bread crumbs, egg, garlic, oregano, basil, salt, and pepper until combined. Set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat oven to 400\u00b0F (200\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Line two empty ice trays with bacon, overlapping each piece to cover the tray completely.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Press the bacon down into each round with two fingers.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Spoon some of the meatball mixture into each round and press down to smooth. Make sure to pack the meat down to touch the bottom of the ice tray.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fold the edges of the bacon on top of the ice tray.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Flip the ice tray over onto a baking sheet and carefully lift the ice cube tray off of the meatballs.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 20 minutes, or until bacon is just brown.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Brush the meatballs with barbecue sauce and bake for 10 minutes, or until the bacon is crispy and meatballs are cooked through.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer the meatball sheet to a cutting board and cut the bacon to create single meatballs.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place a toothpick in each meatball.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"BBQ Bacon Ice Tray Meatballs Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: ground beef, yellow onion, fresh parsley, bread crumbs, egg, garlic, dried oregano, dried basil, salt, pepper, bacon, BBQ sauce\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/135759.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-02-08T00:34:00\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M51S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/77454/landscape_720/1518118860\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"96\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"42\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/bacon-wrapped-parmesan-garlic-knots", "Title": "Bacon-Wrapped Parmesan Garlic Knots", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Bacon-Wrapped Parmesan Garlic Knots Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/148264.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: warm water, active dry yeast, all-purpose flour, grated parmesan cheese, sugar, baking powder, kosher salt, dried basil, dried oregano, olive oil, bacon, unsalted butter, garlic, fresh parsley, marinara sauce\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Bake\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2018-04-05T18:23:19\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"30 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1\u2153 cups warm water\"\n        \n          ,\"1\u00bd teaspoons active dry yeast\"\n        \n          ,\"3\u00bd cups all-purpose flour\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup plus 2 teaspoons grated Parmesan cheese, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon baking powder\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon kosher salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon dried basil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon dried oregano\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons olive oil, divided\"\n        \n          ,\"30 bacon strips\"\n        \n          ,\"5 tablespoons unsalted butter, melted\"\n        \n          ,\"4 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon chopped parsley, for serving\"\n        \n          ,\"Marinara sauce, for serving\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add the warm water to a medium bowl. Sprinkle the yeast over the water and let sit for 5 minutes, or until mixture is frothy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large bowl, whisk together the flour, Parmesan cheese, sugar, baking powder, salt, basil, and oregano.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add 2 tablespoons of olive oil and the yeast-water mixture. Mix with a rubber spatula until a ball of dough forms.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Dump the dough out onto a clean surface and knead for about 5 minutes, until the dough is springy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Grease the large bowl with the remaining tablespoon of olive oil. Place the dough in the bowl, cover with plastic wrap, and let rise in a warm place for 1 hour, or until doubled in size.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the oven to 425\u00b0F (220\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Sprinkle a bit of flour over the dough then dump onto a clean surface. Tear the dough into 30 separate pieces, then roll into 6-inch (15-cm) long strips.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place a strip of bacon over each dough strip. Tie both together to form a knot.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place the knots on a wire rack placed over a baking sheet.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Bake for 20 minutes, or until bread is golden brown and the bacon is crispy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a small bowl, mix together the butter, garlic, and remaining 2 teaspoons of Parmesan cheese.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Brush the knots with the butter mixture and bake for another 5 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Transfer to a serving plate. Garnish with chopped parsley.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve with marinara sauce alongside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Bacon-Wrapped Parmesan Garlic Knots Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: warm water, active dry yeast, all-purpose flour, grated parmesan cheese, sugar, baking powder, kosher salt, dried basil, dried oregano, olive oil, bacon, unsalted butter, garlic, fresh parsley, marinara sauce\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/video-api/assets/148264.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2018-04-05T18:23:19\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M49S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/88195/landscape_720/1522953013\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"97\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"28\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/grilled-potato-volcanoes", "Title": "Grilled Potato Volcanoes", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Grilled Potato Volcanoes Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/3b8cd98a11fa4bf7961450801f48be15/BFV11660_GrilledPotatoVolcanoes-ThumbTextless1080.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: large russet potato, grated cheddar cheese, cream cheese, green onion, bacon, sour cream, green onion\",\n     \"keywords\": \"grill, potato, cheese, creamy, bacon\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Grill\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-04-26T19:45:55\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"6 large russet potatoes\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cups cheddar cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"8 ounces cream cheese\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup green onions\"\n        \n          ,\"12 slices of bacon\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"Sour Cream\"\n        \n          ,\"Green Onions\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Preheat the grill to 400\u02daF (200\u02daC).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Thoroughly scrub the potatoes and poke a few holes in them to vent. Wrap in aluminum foil and place on the grill over direct heat to cook for 20 minutes.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In the meantime, mix 1 \u00bd cups (150g) of cheddar cheese, the cream cheese, and green onions in a medium bowl until well-combined. Set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Remove the potatoes from the grill and let them rest until they are cool enough to handle. Unwrap each potato and cut off the ends so they can stand up. Using a melon baller or a spoon, carve out the center of each potato, being careful not to make the walls too thin, and to leave a bit of thickness at the bottom as well. Fill the potatoes with the cheese mixture and wrap 2 slices of bacon around each one. Secure the bacon with toothpicks, if necessary.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Reduce the grill temperature to about 350\u02daF (175\u02daC) and place the potatoes on the grill over indirect heat for 30 minutes with the lid closed.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"After 30 minutes, top the potatoes with the remaining cheddar cheese and cook for another 15 minutes. Before serving, garnish with a dollop of sour cream and some green onions.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Grilled Potato Volcanoes Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: large russet potato, grated cheddar cheese, cream cheese, green onion, bacon, sour cream, green onion\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/video-api-prod/assets/3b8cd98a11fa4bf7961450801f48be15/BFV11660_GrilledPotatoVolcanoes-ThumbTextless1080.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-04-26T19:45:55\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/8554/mp4_720x1280/1472566853\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"83\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"28\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/mint-chocolate-snack-mix", "Title": "Mint Chocolate Snack Mix", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Mint Chocolate Snack Mix Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/89d7cd6b48cd42fc8f123b324301b8f6/snack_4_way-FB_final.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: peppermint extract, rice cereal, powdered sugar, cocoa powder, mint chocolate candy, semi sweet chocolate, coconut oil\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"totalTime\": \"PT30M\",\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Snacks\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"American\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-11T02:52:23\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"6 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"1 teaspoon peppermint extract\"\n        \n          ,\"5 cups rice cereal\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup powdered sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup cocoa powder\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup mint chocolate candies\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"1 \u00bd cups semisweet chocolate\"\n        \n          ,\"1 teaspoon coconut oil\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a medium bowl, mix coconut oil and chocolate. Melt in microwave for 60 seconds. Stir every 15 seconds until melted.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Add extract into melted chocolate.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Place cereal in large bowl. Mix in melted chocolate and stir until evenly coated.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a large plastic bag, add powdered sugar and cocoa powder.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Close and shake until each cereal is coated with sugar. Add in mint chocolate candies.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Mint Chocolate Snack Mix Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: peppermint extract, rice cereal, powdered sugar, cocoa powder, mint chocolate candy, semi sweet chocolate, coconut oil\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/89d7cd6b48cd42fc8f123b324301b8f6/snack_4_way-FB_final.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T02:52:23\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/14246/mp4_720x1280/1478649778\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"92\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"25\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/japanese-popcorn-chicken-karaage", "Title": "Japanese Popcorn Chicken (Karaage)", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Japanese Popcorn Chicken (Karaage) Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/f8c61fb74cda402bb29472baf0606a66/BFV14278_FriedChickenFromAroundTheWorld3.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Crispy, delicious fried chicken is one of life\u2019s greatest pleasures, but every once in a while, you feel the desire to mix things up. That\u2019s where this recipe for Japanese popcorn chicken steps into the picture. It\u2019s everything you love about fried chicken but what a Japanese kick, thanks to a handful of ingredients like garlic, ginger, sake, soy sauce, and sesame oil. They\u2019re the perfect way to spice up game day\u2026or any day.\",\n     \"keywords\": \"fried chicken\"\n   \n     \"cookTime\": \"PT20M\",\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Japanese\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Deep-Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-11T20:11:14\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"2 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"3 boneless chicken thighs, chopped into 1-inch chunks\"\n        \n          ,\"3 cloves garlic, finely minced\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons ginger, finely grated or minced\"\n        \n          ,\"3 tablespoons soy sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons sake\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon sesame oil\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon sugar\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup potato starch\"\n        \n          ,\"Oil, for frying\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"Lemon wedges and parsley to serve\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Combine the chicken with the garlic, ginger, soy, sake, sesame oil, and sugar in a bowl until evenly coated. Cover and refrigerate for about 1 hour.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat oil in a pot over high heat until about 340\u00b0F (170\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Give the chicken a stir to re-incorporate the marinade, then sprinkle the potato starch on top. Lightly toss until somewhat combined, but do not mix until each chicken piece is evenly coated because the uneven pockets of potato starch will give the chicken its signature unique texture.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fry half of the chicken at a time, until light golden and bubbly, about 5-7 minutes. The oil temperature will drop to about 320\u00b0F (160\u00b0C). Rest the chicken on paper towels and increase the heat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat oil to about 390\u00b0F (200\u00b0C), then fry the chicken again for about 2-3 minutes until golden brown. Drain the chicken on paper towels.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Serve with lemon and parsley.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Japanese Popcorn Chicken (Karaage) Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Crispy, delicious fried chicken is one of life\u2019s greatest pleasures, but every once in a while, you feel the desire to mix things up. That\u2019s where this recipe for Japanese popcorn chicken steps into the picture. It\u2019s everything you love about fried chicken but what a Japanese kick, thanks to a handful of ingredients like garlic, ginger, sake, soy sauce, and sesame oil. They\u2019re the perfect way to spice up game day\u2026or any day.\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/f8c61fb74cda402bb29472baf0606a66/BFV14278_FriedChickenFromAroundTheWorld3.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T20:11:14\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/16094/mp4_720x1280/1480448439\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"98\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"39\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n      }\n  }\n"}
{"URL": "https://tasty.co/recipe/spicy-korean-chicken", "Title": "Spicy Korean Chicken", "Content": "\n{\n   \"@context\": \"http://schema.org/\",\n   \"@type\": \"Recipe\",\n   \"name\": \"Spicy Korean Chicken Recipe by Tasty\",\n   \"image\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/8ca80aec6f49435a87f8c0419c4bc4c7/BFV14278_FriedChickenFromAroundTheWorld3.jpg\",\n   \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chicken wings, cornstarch, oil, sesame seeds, cornstarch, flour, salt, water, soy sauce, honey, rice vinegar, gochujang, garlic, ginger\",\n     \"keywords\": \"fried chicken\"\n   \n   \"author\": {\n     \"@type\": \"Person\",\n     \"name\": \"Tasty\"\n    },\n    \"publisher\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n      \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n      \"logo\": {\n        \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n        \"url\": \"/static-assets/img/favicon.b3bba8bf837f3cc2436736a18d4c4e6d.ico\"\n      }\n    },\n      \"recipeCategory\": \"Appetizers\",\n      \"recipeCuisine\": \"Korean\",\n      \"cookingMethod\": \"Pan Fry\",\n\n    \"datePublished\": \"2017-07-11T20:11:14\",\n    \"recipeYield\": \"2 servings\",\n    \"recipeIngredient\": [\n        \n          \"10 chicken wings and drumettes\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup cornstarch\"\n        \n          ,\"Oil, for frying\"\n        \n          ,\"n/a\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup cornstarch\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bd cup flour\"\n        \n          ,\"2 teaspoons salt\"\n        \n          ,\"1 cup water\"\n        \n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons soy sauce\"\n        \n          ,\"\u00bc cup honey\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons rice vinegar\"\n        \n          ,\"2 tablespoons Korean chili paste (gochujang)\"\n        \n          ,\"2 cloves garlic, minced\"\n        \n          ,\"1 tablespoon ginger, grated\"\n        \n    ],\n    \"recipeInstructions\": [\n        {\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Mix the ingredients for the batter in a bowl until smooth with no lumps.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat oil in a pot to 340\u00b0F (170\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Dip a chicken wing into the cornstarch, shaking off excess, then dredge the wing into the batter, dripping off excess.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fry half of the wings at a time for about 5-7 minutes, until light golden. The oil will drop to about 320\u00b0F (160\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Drain the wings and increase the heat. Heat oil to about 375\u00b0F (190\u00b0C).\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fry the wings a second time until golden brown and crispy. Drain and set aside.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a pan, combine all the ingredients for the sauce and stir until bubbling. Toss in the wings.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"Spicy Korean Chicken Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: chicken wings, cornstarch, oil, sesame seeds, cornstarch, flour, salt, water, soy sauce, honey, rice vinegar, gochujang, garlic, ginger\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/8ca80aec6f49435a87f8c0419c4bc4c7/BFV14278_FriedChickenFromAroundTheWorld3.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-07-11T20:11:14\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT00M00S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co