ls.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Dip a piece of chicken into the flour, then the egg, then back into the flour. Repeat with the rest of the chicken.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Heat oil in a large pot over medium-high heat.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Fry the chicken pieces until deep-golden brown and crispy.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Set aside on a paper towel to drain.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"In a pan over medium heat, cook the BBQ sauce until bubbly.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Toss the chicken in the sauce until evenly glazed.\"\n        }\n        ,{\n          \"@type\": \"HowToStep\",\n          \"text\": \"Enjoy!\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"video\": [{\n      \"name\": \"BBQ Chicken Poppers Recipe by Tasty\",\n      \"description\": \"Here's what you need: boneless, skinless chicken breast, salt, pepper, garlic powder, chili powder, flour, egg, oil, BBQ sauce\",\n      \"thumbnailUrl\": \"https://img.buzzfeed.com/thumbnailer-prod-us-east-1/16c3096f28f44caf9fe38ad8538b9049/BFV12921_ChickenPoppers4Ways-FB1080SQ.jpg\",\n      \"uploadDate\": \"2017-12-17T20:34:07\",\n      \"duration\": \"PT01M44S\",\n      \"publisher\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n        \"name\": \"Tasty\",\n        \"logo\": {\n          \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n          \"url\": \"https://tasty.co/favicon.ico\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"contentUrl\": \"https://vid.tasty.co/output/82507/landscape_720/1520287071\"\n    }],\n      \"aggregateRating\": {\n        \"@type\": \"AggregateRating\",\n        \"ratingValue\": \"97\",\n        \"ratingCount\": \"102\",\n        \"bestRating\": \"100\",\n        \"worstRating\": \"0\"\n  